Package pl.polsl.model

Class ModelTest

java.lang.Object
pl.polsl.model.ModelTest
class ModelTest extends Object
Model Testing Test Class for MatrixCalculatorModel. This class contains unit tests to validate the functionality of matrix addition, subtraction, and multiplication in the model.
Version:
1.2
Author:
MIKOLAJ

    • parseMatrix

      private List<List<Integer>> parseMatrix(List<List<String>> matrix)
      Helper method to parse a matrix of strings into a matrix of integers. This method attempts to convert all elements to integers, simulating the behavior of the model when processing input.
      Parameters:
      matrix - the matrix of strings to parse
      Returns:
      a parsed matrix of integers
      Throws:
      NumberFormatException - if any entry is non-numeric
